<div class="white_box_shadow"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13067567/skicanada.jpg" alt="Save 20% on Lift Passes &amp; £50 off per person at selected hotels in Canada with Inghams" rel="486,324" /></div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g12">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><u>April 2018 Is Inghams Canada Month!<br />Save 20% On Lift Passes And £50 Off Per Person On Selected Hotels In Banff And Whistler For The Winter 2018/19 Ski Season</u></strong></p>
<p><strong>Tuesday 10<sup>th</sup> April 2018 -</strong> Throughout the month of April 2018, leading ski tour operator Inghams is celebrating Canada as one of the world’s top ski destinations, with some special offers to Banff and Whistler for the Winter 2018/19 ski season.</p>
<p>For new bookings <strong>made before 30<sup>th</sup> April 2018</strong>, offers include 20% off the price of the Tri-Area Lift Pass in Banff and 20% off the price of the Whole Area Lift Pass in Whistler. Guests can also take advantage of £50 off per person on selected hotels in Banff (Banff Inn Hotel / Caribou Lodge) and Whistler (Coast Blackcomb Suites / Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites) when booked before 30<sup>th</sup> April 2018. The offers are valid on all departure dates throughout the winter season.                 <br /><br />The Canadian ski experience is unique, with gorgeous panoramas typifying the country’s ski resorts, as well as the opportunity to spot wildlife such as moose. Inghams offers ski holidays to seven of the best ski resorts in Canada, including iconic West Coast gems such as Whistler - which boasts an enviable snow record and incredible infrastructure - and the beautiful resort of Banff - located within the Banff National Park. Both are considered some of Canada’s most popular destinations for British skiers.       </p>
<p><strong><u>Banff</u></strong><br />Inghams is offering a seven-night holiday on a room-only basis at the four-star Caribou Lodge in Banff, Canada, from £947 per person, based on four travelling in January 2018. Price represents the £50 discount per person and includes return flights from London Heathrow to Calgary and airport transfers. Lift passes (including a 20% discount on Tri-Area lift passes), equipment hire and tuition can be pre-booked through Inghams. To book, visit www.inghams.co.uk/skicanada or call 01483 791 114.   </p>
<p><strong><u>Whistler</u></strong> <br />Inghams is offering a seven-night holiday on a room-only basis at the four-star Crystal Lodge &amp; Suites in Whistler, Canada, from £1,090 per person, based on four travelling in January 2018. Price represents the £50 discount per person and includes return flights from London Heathrow to Vancouver and airport transfers. Lift passes (including a 20% discount on Whole Area lift passes), equipment hire and tuition can be pre-booked through Inghams. To book, visit www.inghams.co.uk/skicanada or call 01483 791 114.   </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>-ENDS-</strong></p>
<p><strong><u>ABOUT INGHAMS</u>           </strong><br />Inghams was founded by Walter Ingham in 1934, born out of his enduring passion for ski, mountaineering and walking. In 2014, Inghams celebrated its 80<sup>th</sup> year and the brand continues to pride itself on being one of the UK's leading, most experienced specialist tour operators, delivering a wide range of award-winning holidays to its loyal guests. Today, Inghams offers winter holidays to over 90 resorts in eight countries, with flights from 21 UK regional airports. It also has a popular Lakes &amp; Mountains summer holiday programme to many European destinations and a dedicated Inghams Italy programme. For more information, visit www.inghams.co.uk.         </p>
<p><strong>For media enquiries, please contact Frankie Gibson, PR Executive, on 01483 791 045 / </strong><strong>Frankie.gibson@inghams.co.uk</strong><strong> / Twitter: @Fr4nkie_90<br /><br /></strong></p>
<p>Follow Inghams on social media at:          <br /><strong>Facebook and Twitter:</strong> @InghamsSki / @InghamsSummer / @InghamsItaly       <br /><strong>Instagram:          </strong>         @InghamsHolidays / @InghamsItaly      <br /><strong>YouTube:</strong>                      /inghamsholidays</p>
